         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">3/11/83 ¶  ¶ Today, dear Doctor Leibius, I have forwarded some volumes of my works to you, thereby completing the series of them in your Society's library, and I added a formal answer to you letter. ¶...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">83.11.03a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Adolph<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Leibius</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">ML MSS<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>9077,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Box 65,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Royal Society of NSW papers, Mitchell Library, State Library of NSW, Sydney.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annotated:<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>'Ansd Nov 7. 83'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>3/11/83.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Heute, lieber Herr Doctor Leibius, habe ich an Sie einige Bände meiner Werke adressirt, um dadurch die Reihe derselben in Ihrer Gesellschafts Bibliothek zu vervollständigen, u. fügte ich eine formelle Antwort auf Ihr Schreiben bei.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nun möchte ich noch bemerken, dass es nur eines Briefes an die Regierung von West-Australien zu Perth bedürfte, um auch von dort aus diese Werke über die Pflanzen Australiens zu ergänzen. Es ist nämlich in der Regierungsdruckerei in Perth W.A. ein Rapport über die "Forest resources of Western Australia" von mir erschienen mit 20 Quart-Tafeln, auch sind in demselben Bureau 2 Abhandlungen über Mr Forrest's West Australische Pflanzen Sammlungen gedruckt. Alles Dieses würde Ihrer Gesellschafts Bibliothek bereitwillig zugewandt werden, falls Sie sich an den Hon the Colonial Secretary, Perth, W.A. desshalb wenden wollen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Bestens grüssend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hier sind eben 80 Quart-Zeichnungen fertig geworden über Myoporinen <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Australiens, die auch reichlich in N.S.W. verteten sind; aber die Mittel für das Lithographiren u Drucken werden wohl erst in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1884 u<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1885 erlangt werden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3/11/83</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Today, dear Doctor Leibius, I have forwarded some volumes of my works to you, thereby completing the series of them in your Society's library, and I added a formal answer to you letter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Now I would like to add that it would only need a letter to the Government of Western Australia at Perth to also complete from there these works on the plants of Australia. You see, in the government printing office in Perth, W.A., a report by me with 20 quarto plates has appeared on the "Forest resources of Western Australia".<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B79.13.10<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had been reissued as part of the WA Government report, see B82.13.21</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Also 2 essays on Mr Forrest's West Australian plant collections were printed in the same office.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>John Forrest;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>B81.03.02, B83.08.01.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>All of them could be readily obtained for your Society's library, if you wish to apply to the Hon. the Colonial Secretary, Perth, W.A. for that purpose.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Best greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">About 80 quarto drawings have been prepared here on the Myoporinae of Australia, which also are represented abundantly in N.S.W.; but the funds for the lithography and printing will probably be obtained only in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1884 and<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1885.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's volume of illustrations of the Myoporinae was published in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1886 (B86.08.05).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
